### Lookup Instructions for AI Agents

1. **When asked to use a specific component**: Read `src/ui/<ComponentName>/<ComponentName>.ai.md` to understand its props, patterns, and constraints before writing any code.
2. **When building a feature that combines multiple components**: Read the `.ai.md` file for each component you plan to use. Pay special attention to the "Composition" sections which describe how components work together.
3. **When unsure which component to use**: Refer to the "Available Components" section below, then read the `.ai.md` files of candidate components to compare their intended use cases.
4. **When customizing styles**: Read the component's `.ai.md` file for CSS class references and design token usage, then consult `src/styles/tokens.css` for available token values.

## Available Components

### Layout & Structure
- `Accordion` / `AccordionItem` — Expandable content sections
- `UDS` — Full application wrapper with sidebar, panels, modals
- `Card` — Contained content block with optional header/footer
- `Divider` — Visual separator line
- `Flex` — Flexbox layout utility
- `ImageAspect` — Image with aspect ratio constraint
- `Steps` — Step indicator / wizard progress
- `Table` — Data table with sortable/filterable columns
- `Tabs` / `TabItem` — Tabbed navigation

### Navigation
- `ActionMenu` — Contextual action dropdown menu
- `Breadcrumb` — Page hierarchy breadcrumb trail
- `Dropdown` — Select-style dropdown input
- `Menu` — Full sidebar navigation with brand, search, sections
- `Pagination` — Page navigation controls

### Form Controls
- `Button` — Primary action trigger (multiple appearances, sizes, layouts)
- `Checkbox` — Binary toggle with label
- `Chip` — Filter/selection chip with optional icon and badge
- `Datepicker` — Date selection input
- `Field` — Form field wrapper (label, validation, helper text)
- `FileUpload` — File upload with drag-and-drop
- `Input` — Single-line text input
- `PillToggle` — Segmented control / pill toggle
- `Radio` — Radio button selection
- `Slider` — Range slider input
- `Textarea` — Multi-line text input
- `Toggle` — On/off switch

### Data Display
- `Avatar` — User photo or initials circle
- `Badge` — Numeric badge indicator
- `DotStatus` — Colored status dot
- `Icon` — Phosphor icon wrapper (1000+ icons available)
- `Key` — Keyboard shortcut indicator
- `ProgressCircle` — Circular progress indicator
- `ProgressIndicator` — Linear progress bar
- `Status` — Status label with colored dot
- `Tag` — Colored label tag

### Feedback
- `Toast` — Notification message (success, error, warning, info)
- `Tooltip` — Hover tooltip

### Branding
- `Branding` — Brand logo and identity display

### Utilities
- `MicroCalendar` — Compact calendar widget
- `Playground` — Interactive component playground
